videos.description: Maryland's Brianna Fraser gets the block and Destiny Slocum goes down court and draws the foul for the and-1.
videos.headline: Maryland turns block into And-1 opportunity

videos.description: Maryland's Destiny Slocum goes through the Indiana defenders to finish with the great layup.
videos.headline: Slocum slices through defenders for the layup

videos.description: Maryland's Shatori Walker-Kimbrough hits a buzzer beating 3-pointer from around 70 feet at the end of the third quarter.
videos.headline: Maryland hits 70-foot shot at the buzzer of the 3rd
